Class Name

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.onix2.Name
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnixComposite, OnixComposite.OnixSuperComposite, Serializable

    public class Name
extends Object
implements OnixComposite.OnixSuperComposite, Serializable

    Name composite

    A repeatable group of data elements which together represent a personal name, and specify its type. The <Name> composite may be used to send alternate names for the same person, eg to handle such cases as Ian Rankin writing as Jack Harvey.

    Reference name <Name>
    Short tag <name>
